    "Threat models and attack vectors are considered untargeted with the adversary's intention to reduce the overall accuracy of the targeted model.",
    "Targeted attacks can not be the scenario with the black box attack model, as the adversary does not know the victim model to exploit it with a specific targeted attack vector.",
